<!-- ═══ WHY SIBU — 4 clean cards ══════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="lp-section">
    <div class="lp-container">
        <div class="lp-section-head">
            <div>
                <span class="lp-section-kicker">What makes Sibu special</span>
                <h2 class="lp-section-h2">Four flavours of one city</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-why-grid">
            <div class="lp-why-card lp-why-card--nature mk-fade-in">
                <div class="lp-why-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
                    @* Pine / leaf — nature *@
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M12 2 L5 11 H8 L4 17 H8 L4 22 H20 L16 17 H20 L16 11 H19 Z"/>
                        <line x1="12" y1="22" x2="12" y2="18"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Living rainforest</h3>
                <p>Bukit Lima's primary jungle, hornbills overhead, the wide green Rajang at every turn. Sibu is a city where nature is never more than five minutes away.</p>
                <span class="lp-why-tag">Nature</span>
            </div>
            <div class="lp-why-card lp-why-card--heritage mk-fade-in mk-fade-in-1">
                <div class="lp-why-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
                    @* Classical column / heritage *@
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 9 L12 4 L21 9 Z"/>
                        <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/>
                        <line x1="6" y1="9" x2="6" y2="18"/>
                        <line x1="10" y1="9" x2="10" y2="18"/>
                        <line x1="14" y1="9" x2="14" y2="18"/>
                        <line x1="18" y1="9" x2="18" y2="18"/>
                        <line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/>
                        <line x1="2" y1="21" x2="22" y2="21"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Foochow heritage</h3>
                <p>Tua Pek Kong's century-old altars, Lau King Howe's tiled pavilions, the seven-storey pagoda. Every building tells the story of the pioneers who built Swan City.</p>
                <span class="lp-why-tag">Heritage</span>
            </div>
            <div class="lp-why-card lp-why-card--food mk-fade-in mk-fade-in-2">
                <div class="lp-why-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
                    @* Bowl with chopsticks — cuisine *@
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 12 H21 A9 8 0 0 1 12 20 A9 8 0 0 1 3 12 Z"/>
                        <line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/>
                        <line x1="14" y1="3" x2="20" y2="11"/>
                        <line x1="17" y1="3" x2="22" y2="9"/>
                        <path d="M7 9 Q9 6 11 9" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Foochow cuisine</h3>
                <p>Kampua mee at dawn, Kompia from the wood-fired oven, Kolo mee with crispy lard. Sibu's food scene is one of Malaysia's best-kept secrets.</p>
                <span class="lp-why-tag">Food</span>
            </div>
            <div class="lp-why-card lp-why-card--river mk-fade-in mk-fade-in-3">
                <div class="lp-why-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
                    @* River waves with mountain *@
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 7 L8 13 L12 9 L21 18 H3 Z" fill="currentColor" fill-opacity="0.12"/>
                        <path d="M3 7 L8 13 L12 9 L21 18"/>
                        <path d="M2 16 Q5 14 8 16 T14 16 T20 16"/>
                        <path d="M2 20 Q5 18 8 20 T14 20 T20 20"/>
                        <circle cx="17" cy="5" r="1.5"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Rajang river life</h3>
                <p>Express boats upriver, fishing villages on stilts, sunrise over the longest river in Malaysia. The Rajang is Sibu's lifeblood and its greatest spectacle.</p>
                <span class="lp-why-tag">Adventure</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ QUOTE BREAK 1 — Rajang River ═════════════════════════ -->
<div class="lp-quote-break" style="background-image:url('/Images/rajang-river.jpg');" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="lp-quote-break-overlay"></div>
    <div class="lp-quote-break-body">
        <span class="lp-quote-tag">Rajang River · Sibu · Sarawak</span>
        <p class="lp-quote-text">"Malaysia's longest river flows right through Sibu's heart."</p>
        <p class="lp-quote-attr">Swan City &nbsp;·&nbsp; Sarawak &nbsp;·&nbsp; Borneo</p>
